    "body": "### Problem\n\nhttps://github.com/user-attachments/assets/963a0cc7-f57a-4851-a5f6-73535645277b\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n`nvim --clean -u minimal.lua`,\n\nminimal.lua:\n\n```lua\nrequire(\"vim._extui\").enable({\n\tmsg = {\n\t\tpos = \"box\",\n\t},\n})\n\nlocal t = {\n\ta = 1,\n\tb = 2,\n}\n\nlocal timer = vim.uv.new_timer()\ntimer:start(\n\t0,\n\t1000,\n\tfunction()\n\t\tvim.print(t)\n\tend\n)\n```\n\nthe shrinking also occurs when done manually\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nnot shrink\n\n### Nvim version (nvim -v)\n\nNVIM v0.12.0-dev-303+g627c648252\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nno\n\n### Operating system/version\n\n6.14.4-arch1-1\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nst 0.8.5\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\nst-256color\n\n### Installation\n\nAUR",
